### 用户登录：普通用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test01",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 用户登录：管理员
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin01",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test03",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "13800138003"
}

### 获取个人信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/info
token: 替换成登录返回的token

### 树木列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tree/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
token: 替换成登录返回的token

### 树木详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tree/detail?treeId=1
token: 替换成登录返回的token

### 用户认养树木
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/create
Content-Type: application/json
token: 替换成普通用户token

{
  "treeId": 2,
  "cycleMonth": 12
}

### 我的树
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/myTree
token: 替换成普通用户token

### 管理员新增树木
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tree/add
Content-Type: application/json
token: 替换成管理员token

{
  "companyId": 1,
  "treeType": "樱花树",
  "position": "一号农田 A 区 008",
  "price": 240,
  "status": 0,
  "coverImg": "/static/tree/demo.svg",
  "cameraSn": "CAM-A008",
  "cameraIp": "192.168.1.108",
  "camUser": "admin",
  "camPwd": "123456"
}

### 管理员订单列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/all?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
token: 替换成管理员token

### 摄像头状态
GET http://localhost:8080/api/camera/status/list
token: 替换成管理员token

### 抓拍
GET http://localhost:8080/api/camera/snapshot?treeId=1
token: 替换成普通用户token

### 视频流
GET http://localhost:8080/api/camera/rtsp?treeId=1
token: 替换成普通用户token

### 手动抓拍
POST http://localhost:8080/api/camera/manualCap
Content-Type: application/json
token: 替换成管理员token

{
  "treeId": 1
}
